# Optional Common Access Card (CAC) Authentication Server for Microgrid Planner

# File organization

├── cac-server/
│   ├── Dockerfile.template                 <- Dockerfile template for the CAC server, adjust as needed
│   ├── default.conf.template               <- NGINX configuration file template, adjust as needed
│   └── certs
│       ├── server.crt                      <- Valid certs
│       ├── server.key                      <- Valid certs
│       └── dod-ca-bundle.pem               <- Configuration files from https://www.cyber.mil/pki-pke/tools-configuration-files

## CAC Server Setup Instructions

1. Generate `server.crt` and `server.key` certificates (or equivalent .pem files)
1. Copy templates to actual files and update files referenced as needed:
   - `cp cac-server/Dockerfile.template cac-server/Dockerfile`
   - `cp cac-server/default.conf.template cac-server/default.conf`
